Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:34.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  露丝\N{\rEng}Hey, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  黛娜\N{\rEng}Hey, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找他\N{\rEng}I'm gonna go over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.71,0:05:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等你\N{\rEng}We're waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\rEng}Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:22.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史崔特  阿尔文\N{\rEng}Alvin Straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝两个钟前出去了\N{\rEng}Rose left a couple of hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有大声叫露丝吗\N{\rEng}Did you hear me hollerin' for Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是找她\N{\rEng}I wasn't lookin' for Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今日没见过阿尔文\N{\rEng}I haven't seen Alvin today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有问吗\N{\rEng}Did I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史崔特  你迟到了\N{\rEng}Straight, you're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-进来老友  -阿尔文你这是...\N{\rEng}-Come in, Bud. -What the...Alvin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟在哪里\N{\rEng}Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都看不见\N{\rEng}I can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老友  这里\N{\rEng}Over here, Bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你脚下\N{\rEng}Watch your step.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在干嘛\N{\rEng}What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在地上做什么\N{\rEng}What are you doin' layin' on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻呀  你一个钟前该去到酒吧\N{\rEng}You nuts? Supposed to be down at Davmar's one hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\rEng}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐！\N{\rEng}Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿  黛娜\N{\rEng}Hey, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,911的号码是多少\N{\rEng}What's the number for 911?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  黛娜\N{\rEng}No, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你究竟在干什么\N{\rEng}What are you doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:43.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打去酒吧说  我们不去了\N{\rEng}I'll call the bar and tell 'em we're not comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗  有人中风呀\N{\rEng}Are you crazy? We have a stricken man here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你中风了吗\N{\rEng}Are you stricken, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黛娜  放下电话\N{\rEng}Put the phone down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  你们在吵什么\N{\rEng}Dad, what's all the yellin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  对我爸爸做了什么\N{\rEng}Wh-what...uh, have you done to my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.70,0:08:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有搞错\N{\rEng}Oh, for cry eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEng}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  爸爸\N{\rEng}Are you OK, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:11.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  我需要人扶我起来\N{\rEng}I just need a little help gettin' up, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先去酒吧  马上回来\N{\rEng}I'm goin' to Davmar's. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}OK, Bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.16,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去\N{\rEng}I'm not goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEng}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不去\N{\rEng}I'm not goin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:02.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  你答应过我\N{\rEng}You promised me, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史崔特先生  脱下衣服然后穿上袍子\N{\rEng}OK, Mr Straight, put this robe on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫医生来就行了\N{\rEng}Just bring me the doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢鸟儿\N{\rEng}You like birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我建...小鸟屋...给小鸟的屋子\N{\rEng}I build...uh, birdhouses... uh, for bluebirds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那很好\N{\rEng}Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得  他...出售我做的小鸟屋\N{\rEng}Yeah, it's Pete...uh, Pete sells my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得的五金铺..有我的小鸟屋卖\N{\rEng}uh, birdhouses... at the Ace Hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次去一定留意\N{\rEng}I'll look for them next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要手术\N{\rEng}No operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早你跌倒起不来  是你盘骨有问题\N{\rEng}This morning you fall and can't get up, that's your hips, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要用助行架\N{\rEng}And you'll need a walker now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要助行架\N{\rEng}No walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那加多一枝手杖\N{\rEng}Fine, a second cane, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你视觉模糊\N{\rEng}You say you're having trouble seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是糖尿病引发\N{\rEng}That could be a diabetes-related problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:36.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做些检查\N{\rEng}I'd like to run some tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不检查  我们不够钱照x光\N{\rEng}No tests and no X-rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:44.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见你吸烟\N{\rEng}Well, I see and hear that you smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估你是早期肺气肿\N{\rEng}My guess is you're in the early stages of emphysema.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你循环系统又有问题\N{\rEng}And Alvin, you have circulation problems
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.49,0:10:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心你的饮食\N{\rEng}and I'm worried about your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若不尽快改进\N{\rEng}If you don't make some changes quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:11:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有严重的后遗症\N{\rEng}there will be some serious consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是...红屋顶\N{\rEng}It...has a...a red roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  又做了一个相当漂亮的小鸟屋\N{\rEng}Another pretty one, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想下一个屋顶做成蓝色的\N{\rEng}I want to...uh, paint the...uh, next one blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意\N{\rEng}That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生怎么说\N{\rEng}What...uh, did the doctor say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说我长命百岁\N{\rEng}He said I was gonna live to be 100.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去铲草坪\N{\rEng}I think I'll go and mow the lawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:02.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  让我来做\N{\rEng}Uh, I can...uh, cut it for you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以做的  放心\N{\rEng}I got it, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rEng}God darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们今天不能铲草\N{\rEng}No, we'll... we won't be mowin' today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风暴要来了\N{\rEng}Storm's comin' in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最爱闪电暴风雨\N{\rEng}Yeah. I love a lightnin' storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  我也是\N{\rEng}Uh, me too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.68,0:14:53.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗...是露丝\N{\rEng}This is...is Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖尔叔叔...惨啦\N{\rEng}Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候  好...好...我会跟他说\N{\rEng}When? OK...right...right... I'll tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好...再见\N{\rEng}Yeah... OK... Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是波比\N{\rEng}Uh, that was...Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说赖尔叔叔中了风\N{\rEng}Uncle Lyle...had a... ..a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEng}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  波比  他没说什么\N{\rEng}No, Bobby, he...he didn't say much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都很...顽固\N{\rEng}Uh, they've both... uh, been so... uh, stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我记得是更久之前\N{\rEng}No, no, it was longer, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,88年  7月7日\N{\rEng}It was...uh, July, uh, 7th, 19...88, uh, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波比  我一直记得日子\N{\rEng}I always...remember the dates.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道他有什么打算\N{\rEng}I don't know...uh, what he'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  亲爱的\N{\rEng}Rose, darlin'? Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跑一趟\N{\rEng}I'm gonna go back on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  我要跑一趟去见赖尔\N{\rEng}I've gotta go see Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  爸\N{\rEng}But, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\rEng}How are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:08.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没想到\N{\rEng}Well, I...haven't quite got that figured yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一  你视力不好  不能驾车\N{\rEng}One, your eyes are bad. That's why you don't... uh, drive your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二  赖尔叔叔住在  威斯康辛州\N{\rEng}Uh, two, Uncle Lyle... uh, lives in...uh, Wisconsin,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是  三百七十里的路程\N{\rEng}which is...uh, 317 miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.30,0:18:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要在公路上过夜\N{\rEng}You would have to...uh, stay all night...in Des Moines.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且没有巴士到锡安山\N{\rEng}Then there's no... uh, bus...to Zion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三  你盆骨扛不住\N{\rEng}Three, your...uh, hips are bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站两分钟都艰难\N{\rEng}You can hardly...uh, stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你站起来的时候\N{\rEng}for two minutes... And when you...uh, do stand up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:19:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都颤颤巍巍的了\N{\rEng}this...is the sound you make... when you...stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四  你已经73岁了...\N{\rEng}Uh, four, uh, you are...uh, 73 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.47,0:19:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你出生时\N{\rEng}You were...uh, born
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是古列治做美国总统的时代\N{\rEng}when, uh, Calvin...uh, Coolidge was president...of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在你已73岁了  爸爸\N{\rEng}Uh, you are... uh, 73 years old, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不能开车送你\N{\rEng}And...I cannot drive you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  我还没死呢\N{\rEng}Rose, darlin', I'm not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  我们在做什么\N{\rEng}Uh, what are we... uh, building, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开派对去吗\N{\rEng}Havin' a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  派对我喜欢\N{\rEng}Oh, jeez,... I love...uh, parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\rEng}Oh, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里开派对\N{\rEng}And so...where's it at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么哪里\N{\rEng}Where's what at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是要开派对吗\N{\rEng}Your...uh, party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有\N{\rEng}I'm not havin' a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:07.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为你要\N{\rEng}I thought YOU were havin' a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有吗\N{\rEng}I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:12.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多德国肝肠...\N{\rEng}Well, yeah. Look at all that Braunschweiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  很多呵\N{\rEng}Oh, yeah, it's a lot of Braunschweiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸出门需要的\N{\rEng}It's...uh, for my dad, uh, for his...his trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸爸要去  去威斯康辛州\N{\rEng}Uh, my dad... he's going to...uh, Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问他怎么去\N{\rEng}I...asked him how he's...uh, going to get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他什么也不讲\N{\rEng}Uh...but he... uh, won't say nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威斯康辛州  开派对的好地方\N{\rEng}Wisconsin? That is a real party state.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我讨厌吃这肝肠...\N{\rEng}Yeah. I...uh, hate... uh, Braun...uh...schweiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你有3个5加仑的油罐\N{\rEng}Yeah. Alvin, you've got three five-gallon cans there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总共15加仑汽油\N{\rEng}15 gallons of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要这么多汽油做什么\N{\rEng}What do you need so much gas for, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.87,0:21:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是八卦\N{\rEng}Sig, you're one nosey son of a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说到重点了\N{\rEng}You got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要买那家伙\N{\rEng}I wanna buy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  那长钳\N{\rEng}What? The grabber.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呀  阿尔文\N{\rEng}Oh, jeez, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那是我私家钳  -怎样\N{\rEng}-That's MY grabber, Alvin. -Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:53.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呀  阿尔文  我确实有两个\N{\rEng}Oh, jeez, Alvin. I don't... I...I do have two of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出5美元买它\N{\rEng}I think five dollars is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:22:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  这长钳实在是好用  我真舍不得卖\N{\rEng}That's a darn good grabber, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.79,0:22:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样  所以呢\N{\rEng}I...I... Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  可遇而不可求\N{\rEng}They're hard to come by, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.00,0:22:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我订个货都得2个月\N{\rEng}It's gonna take me two months to get another one on order.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:21.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  这样吧  阿尔文  10美元\N{\rEng}Jeez, Alvin, ten dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成交\N{\rEng}Ring her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.78,0:23:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要长钳来做什么\N{\rEng}What do you need that grabber for, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钳\N{\rEng}Grabbin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:23:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呀  爸爸\N{\rEng}Oh, jeez, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.37,0:24:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呀  爸爸\N{\rEng}Oh, jeez, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.78,0:24:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听听那谷仓的旧升降机\N{\rEng}Listen to that old grain elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.61,0:24:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是收割时节了\N{\rEng}It's...uh, harvest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.40,0:24:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拖车  太重了\N{\rEng}Uh, that...uh, trailer is too h-heavy for...for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.83,0:24:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是铲草车  你要开...\N{\rEng}It's a lawn mower. You're going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.19,0:24:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铲草车...去另一个州\N{\rEng}..drive a...a lawn mower to another state?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.98,0:24:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  我一定要去见赖尔\N{\rEng}Rosie, I've... I've gotta go see Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.36,0:25:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我要独自上路\N{\rEng}And I...I've gotta make this trip on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.66,0:25:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你会理解我的\N{\rEng}I know you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.03,0:25:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想是吧\N{\rEng}I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.36,0:25:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  看看天空\N{\rEng}Look up at the sky, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.32,0:25:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的星星很灿烂\N{\rEng}The sky is sure full of stars tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.27,0:26:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文那老家伙  在驾驶他的铲草车\N{\rEng}Crimenetto, it's Alvin and he's driving his lawn mower.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.15,0:26:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你在这做什么啊\N{\rEng}Alvin! What are you settin' out to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.57,0:26:24.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有搞错  阿尔文\N{\rEng}For cry eye, Alvin!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.15,0:26:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  我就怕你\N{\rEng}Alvin, you're gonna get blown right off the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.61,0:26:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在路上给人撞翻\N{\rEng}that's what I'm afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.40,0:26:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他连格罗托都过不去\N{\rEng}He'll never make it past The Grotto.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.43,0:31:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎有点问题\N{\rEng}I'm havin' a little engine trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.22,0:31:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一架力士  可否载我入城\N{\rEng}It's a Rehds. Could you give me a lift into town?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.18,0:31:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我载你到格罗托  这是阳光旅行团  上来吧\N{\rEng}Yeah, to The Grotto. This is the Sun Ray Tour. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.97,0:32:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我到那里找人帮你  -太感激你了\N{\rEng}-I'll get you help there. -I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.14,0:32:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的爱德华也喜欢骑着他的铲草车\N{\rEng}My Edward loved his riding mower.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.21,0:33:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快来呀  快来\N{\rEng}Hey, come here, hurry. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.09,0:33:18.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的阿尔文\N{\rEng}Poor Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.46,0:33:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小型货车...的人  带我爸爸回来\N{\rEng}So the man...in a...pick-up, he brought my dad back.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定得去美容院\N{\rEng}Ohh...mm, I must've been at the beauty shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.05,0:33:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么车\N{\rEng}What kinda pick-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.84,0:34:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福特\N{\rEng}A Ford.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.34,0:34:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你爸爸为何拿着枪  不知道\N{\rEng}But what's your dad doin' with that gun? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.25,0:34:21.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上次不是卖那架旧力士给你吗  对吗\N{\rEng}I gave you that old Rehds last time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.71,0:34:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀\N{\rEng}That you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.42,0:34:26.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用力士来换一架新的吗\N{\rEng}You tradin' in that Rehds now?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.41,0:34:29.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我相信不会\N{\rEng}No, I don't believe I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.04,0:34:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得跟我说你要用它作特殊用途\N{\rEng}Pete told me you used that rider in a real interestin' way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.76,0:34:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有这打算不\N{\rEng}You still plannin' to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.59,0:34:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  我仍有这打算\N{\rEng}Yeah, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.62,0:34:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道要你改变主意是不可能的\N{\rEng}I know not to talk you out of something you set your mind to,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.19,0:34:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要告诉你  我一直都觉得你是个聪明人\N{\rEng}but Alvin, you've always struck me as smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.75,0:34:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢你  汤姆\N{\rEng}Well, that's appreciated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.83,0:34:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来\N{\rEng}Until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.83,0:34:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么年份的\N{\rEng}What year?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,66年\N{\rEng}'66.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.42,0:35:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高拿引擎\N{\rEng}Kohler engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.72,0:35:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前是拿来做配件\N{\rEng}We've used it for parts
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.71,0:35:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新零件一到就换下了\N{\rEng}but I always replace them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.78,0:35:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部很好\N{\rEng}The guts are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.16,0:35:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没猫腻  有内置变压器\N{\rEng}It's got the old transmission. Nothing fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.08,0:35:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-性能好吗  -很好\N{\rEng}-Is it a good machine? -It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.55,0:35:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤姆  我只有325元\N{\rEng}Tom, I got $325.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.04,0:35:19.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有那么多\N{\rEng}That's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.71,0:35:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受  阿尔文\N{\rEng}Sounds good to me, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.78,0:35:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去办手续吧\N{\rEng}Let's go settle up with Alice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.17,0:35:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点\N{\rEng}One more thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.39,0:35:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果知道上手主人\N{\rEng}sometime you can find out
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.29,0:35:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会更了解它状况\N{\rEng}about these old machines,  if you know who run 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.17,0:35:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道谁是它的前主人吗\N{\rEng}Do you know who owned it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.93,0:35:35.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然知道  就是我\N{\rEng}You bet... Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.50,0:35:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了\N{\rEng}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.94,0:39:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我搭不到顺风车\N{\rEng}I couldn't get a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.16,0:39:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你饿吗\N{\rEng}Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.15,0:39:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么吃的\N{\rEng}Whaddaya got?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.32,0:39:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝肠\N{\rEng}Weeners.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.33,0:39:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝肠\N{\rEng}Weeners?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.07,0:39:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肝肠  要试吗\N{\rEng}Weeners. Wanna try one?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.98,0:39:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这支棍子好用  拿去吧\N{\rEng}Here's a good stick for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.57,0:40:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大一块垃圾\N{\rEng}What a hunk ofjunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.61,0:40:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你的啦  大小姐\N{\rEng}Eat your dinner, missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.89,0:41:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在路上多久了\N{\rEng}So,...how long you been out on the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.69,0:41:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大半生都在路上\N{\rEng}Well, I been travel in most of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.36,0:41:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哪里来的\N{\rEng}Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.90,0:41:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳伦斯\N{\rEng}Laurens.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.23,0:41:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有老婆在那里吗  孩子呢\N{\rEng}Got a wife back there? Kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.65,0:41:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太太弗兰丝生14个  有7个健在\N{\rEng}My wife, Francis delivered 14 babies. Seven of them made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.03,0:41:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿露丝与我同住\N{\rEng}My daughter, Rose lives with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.44,0:42:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗兰丝81年去世了\N{\rEng}Francis died in '81.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.02,0:42:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家人呢\N{\rEng}Where's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.89,0:42:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是离家出走吗\N{\rEng}Are you runnin' away?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.14,0:42:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你离家多久了\N{\rEng}How far along are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.85,0:42:37.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有5个月了\N{\rEng}Five months.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.10,0:42:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去探望我哥哥赖尔\N{\rEng}Well, I'm headin' to see my brother Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.94,0:43:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说要去探望在锡安山的哥哥\N{\rEng}I said I'm goin' to see my brother Lyle in Mount Zion.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.43,0:43:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里  -威斯康辛\N{\rEng}-Where's that? -Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.43,0:43:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额...-过了这个州\N{\rEng}-Oh... -Just across the state line.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.81,0:43:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢老头\N{\rEng}Cheddar Heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.32,0:43:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从没见过吧\N{\rEng}Aren't those the dumbest things
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.35,0:43:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有人戴那么愚蠢的帽子在头上\N{\rEng}you ever seen somebody stick on their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.81,0:43:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说威斯康辛州是个开派对的好地方\N{\rEng}I hear that's a real party place -Wisconsin.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.85,0:43:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该没机会去\N{\rEng}Guess I'll never get to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.89,0:43:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖车里有张毯子  不如你去拿\N{\rEng}There's a blanket in the trailer. Why don't you go get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.27,0:44:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家人会恨死我\N{\rEng}My family hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.01,0:44:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们知道了肯定恨死\N{\rEng}They'll really hate me when they find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.72,0:44:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没告诉他们\N{\rEng}You didn't tell 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.84,0:44:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人知道  \N{\rEng}No. No one knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.96,0:44:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我男朋友都不知道\N{\rEng}Not even my boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.93,0:45:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能生气\N{\rEng}Well, they may be mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.68,0:45:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不至于想失去你\N{\rEng}but I don't think they're mad enough to wanna lose you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.05,0:45:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或你的"小问题"\N{\rEng}or your little problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.93,0:45:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\rEng}I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.18,0:45:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道  但有个温暖的家\N{\rEng}Well, of course, neither do I, but a warm bed and a roof
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.34,0:45:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总好过\N{\rEng}sounds a might better
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.26,0:45:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和一个骑着铲草车赶路的老头\N{\rEng}than eatin' a hot dog on a stick
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.06,0:45:26.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起用支棍子吃热狗\N{\rEng}with an old geezer that's travellin' on a lawn mower.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.59,0:45:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿她...\N{\rEng}My daughter Rose is...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.22,0:45:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多人说我女儿智商低  但她不是\N{\rEng}Some people call her a little bit slow but she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.64,0:45:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她头脑敏锐\N{\rEng}She's got a mind like a bear trap for facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.22,0:45:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做家务井井有条\N{\rEng}She keeps everything organised around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.06,0:45:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好妈妈\N{\rEng}She was a real good mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.59,0:45:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有四个孩子\N{\rEng}She had four kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.59,0:46:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有晚  别人替她照顾小孩时\N{\rEng}One night, somebody else was watchin' the kids
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.97,0:46:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然失火\N{\rEng}and there was a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.42,0:46:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小儿子严重烧伤\N{\rEng}Her second boy got burned real bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.72,0:46:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽不是露丝的错失\N{\rEng}Rose had nothin' to do with it but, ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.26,0:46:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但州政府觉得\N{\rEng}..on account of the way Rose is, the State figured
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.22,0:46:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她无能力照顾孩子\N{\rEng}she wasn't competent to take care of them kids
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.72,0:46:27.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是将孩子带走\N{\rEng}and they took 'em all away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.05,0:46:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她没有一天不挂念她的孩子\N{\rEng}There isn't a day goes by that she don't pine for them kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.38,0:46:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的孩子小时候  我常常跟他们玩个游戏\N{\rEng}When my kids were real little, I used to play a game with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.30,0:46:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人派一支棍子\N{\rEng}I'd give each one of 'em a stick and
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.84,0:47:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后叫他们  将棍子折断\N{\rEng}one for each one of 'em -then I'd say ''you break that.''
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.64,0:47:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然很轻易办到\N{\rEng}'Course they could, real easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.17,0:47:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫他们把棍子绑起来\N{\rEng}Then I'd say ''tie them sticks in a bundle
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.84,0:47:12.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再尝试折断\N{\rEng}and try to break that''.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.88,0:47:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然不成功  然后我说  那就是家人团结的力量\N{\rEng}'Course they couldn't. Then I'd say ''that bundle... ..that's family.''
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.04,0:47:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不如睡拖车\N{\rEng}Why don't you sleep in the trailer?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.80,0:47:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡这里就可以\N{\rEng}This chair'sjust fine for me tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.38,0:47:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  睡这里看星星\N{\rEng}No, I'll be fine sleepin' out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.50,0:47:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有我思考\N{\rEng}Lookin' at the stars helps me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.05,0:48:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.87,0:53:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是...\N{\rEng}What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.99,0:53:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEng}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.78,0:54:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你还好吗  我没事\N{\rEng}Hey, how're you doin'? I'm fine
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.61,0:54:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  爱莲\N{\rEng}Hey, Irene.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.11,0:55:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻时不会想到老年\N{\rEng}You don't think about gettin' old when you're young.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.65,0:55:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该想\N{\rEng}You shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.57,0:55:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老也有老的好处\N{\rEng}Must be something good about gettin' old.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.44,0:55:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额  我无法想象变得又瞎又跛能有什么好的\N{\rEng}Well, I can't imagine anything good about being blind and lame
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.95,0:55:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说如此  但仍然...\N{\rEng}at the same time, but...still
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.23,0:55:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我这个年纪  什么事情都见过了\N{\rEng}at my age, I've seen about all
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.47,0:55:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活必须有舍弃\N{\rEng}that life has to dish out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.03,0:55:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道将小麦从谷壳中分离出来\N{\rEng}I know to separate the wheat
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.20,0:55:40.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记些没用的事情\N{\rEng}from the chaff and let the small stuff fall away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.69,0:55:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  先生\N{\rEng}Let's go, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.73,0:55:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  对于年老的人最坏的是什么  阿尔文你觉得呢\N{\rEng}So, ah...what's the worst part about being old, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.78,0:55:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最坏的就是想起年轻时候的自己\N{\rEng}The worst part of being old is rememberin' when you was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.22,0:58:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士  有什么可以帮助你的\N{\rEng}Can I help you, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.31,0:58:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你帮不了我  谁也帮不了我\N{\rEng}No, you can't help me. No one can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.60,0:58:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经试着把灯开着  狂按喇叭\N{\rEng}I've tried driving with my lights on, sounding my horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.47,0:58:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尖叫  摇下窗户并且敲打车门\N{\rEng}I scream, I roll the window down and bang on the door
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.06,0:58:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还把"公敌"播放得很大声\N{\rEng}and play Public Enemy real loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.35,0:58:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我连春哥都拜过了\N{\rEng}I've prayed to St Francis of Assisi, St Christopher too!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.31,0:58:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真见鬼  我尝试了所有一切\N{\rEng}What the heck! I've tried everything and still every week
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.35,0:58:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是每周至少还是会撞到一头鹿\N{\rEng}I hit at least one deer!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.76,0:58:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,7周内我已经在这条路上撞了13头小鹿\N{\rEng}I have hit 13 deer in seven weeks driving down this road!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.02,0:58:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还必须每天40英里的速度\N{\rEng}And I HAVE to drive down this road every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.52,0:58:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开车从这条路去工作\N{\rEng}40 miles to work and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.02,0:58:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不去工作然后回家\N{\rEng}I HAVE to drive to work and I HAVE to drive home!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.27,0:58:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们从哪儿来\N{\rEng}Where do they come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.97,0:59:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢...已经挂了\N{\rEng}Oh...he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.14,0:59:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那么喜爱鹿\N{\rEng}And I LOVE deer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.92,1:01:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  确实应该找个合适的地方\N{\rEng}Well, they sure picked the right place to practise a burn on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.34,1:01:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里太碍眼了\N{\rEng}That Rumelthanger place was an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.30,1:02:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该做些啥...\N{\rEng}What do you suppose...?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.75,1:02:39.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个割草车吗\N{\rEng}Is that a lawn mower?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.34,1:03:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你还好吗\N{\rEng}Mister, you OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.25,1:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  你该庆幸她没辗着你\N{\rEng}Jeez, mister, you're lucky she didn't roll on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.79,1:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得有什么坏掉了\N{\rEng}I guess the belt broke.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.88,1:03:36.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意料之中\N{\rEng}I wouldn't be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.21,1:03:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那拖车没刹车是吧\N{\rEng}You don't have brakes on that trailer, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.54,1:03:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为农机厂工作30年了\N{\rEng}I worked for John Deere for 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.63,1:03:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该用铲草车拖着拖车下去的\N{\rEng}you shouldn't be hauling a rig behind a mower.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.54,1:03:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不是这样下那种山\N{\rEng}At least not down a hill like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.67,1:03:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是丹尼  瑞丹\N{\rEng}I'm Danny Riordan.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.50,1:03:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  史崔特\N{\rEng}Alvin Straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.26,1:03:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  让我们帮你把这东西停在路边\N{\rEng}Alvin, let's get you and this rig off the road
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.83,1:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看哪里坏了\N{\rEng}and see what the damage is.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.13,1:04:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把它停在这里\N{\rEng}Let's get this off the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.21,1:04:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\rEng}Sure you're OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.04,1:05:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rEng}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.62,1:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以吗  一切都还好吗  那我们回去做事了\N{\rEng}You OK? Everything all right? I'm going back to the exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.04,1:05:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  太感激你了\N{\rEng}Thanks. Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.37,1:05:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们来看看这个机器\N{\rEng}Well,...let's take a look at this mower.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.24,1:05:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是65还是66的机器  -66年的\N{\rEng}-This is what '65, '66? -'66.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.99,1:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我告诉你  阿尔文\N{\rEng}Well,...tell you right now, Alvin,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.96,1:05:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚你哪儿都不能去\N{\rEng}you won't be going anywhere tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.50,1:05:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎都快磨损完了\N{\rEng}Aside from your, ah, drive belt being busted,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.70,1:05:40.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的传动系统也问题\N{\rEng}you got transmission problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.29,1:05:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想去哪儿  -锡安山\N{\rEng}-Where you headed? -Mount Zion.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.67,1:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡安山  威斯康辛州吗  草场过去的那个\N{\rEng}Mount Zion, Wisconsin? Past Prairie du Chien?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.78,1:05:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是60多英里的山\N{\rEng}That's 60 more miles of hills.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.24,1:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要穿过密西西比河\N{\rEng}That's across the Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.16,1:05:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡安山有什么  阿尔文\N{\rEng}What's in Mount Zion, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.62,1:05:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥住在那里\N{\rEng}My brother lives there.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.42,1:05:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你为何不开车去  -我没有驾照\N{\rEng}-Why didn't you take your car? -I'm not licensed.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.83,1:06:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他不能来看你吗  -他中风入院了\N{\rEng}-Couldn't he visit? -He's had a bad stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.04,1:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪儿来\N{\rEng}Where are you coming from?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.32,1:06:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后面\N{\rEng}Back a piece.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.20,1:06:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西部联盟\N{\rEng}West Union?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.58,1:06:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-衣阿华  -不是\N{\rEng}-Hawkeye? -Nope.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.17,1:06:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是新汉普顿吧  你不会是从那么远来的吧\N{\rEng}Well, not New Hampton? You haven't come that far.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.37,1:06:22.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经走了很漫长的路了  是吗\N{\rEng}You've come a long ways, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.62,1:06:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  劳伦斯  爱荷华州\N{\rEng}Yeah, I have. Laurens, Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.78,1:06:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳伦斯\N{\rEng}Laurens?!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.49,1:06:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是西部的格罗托  你在路上多久了\N{\rEng}That's west of The Grotto. How long have you been on the road?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.75,1:06:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天几号\N{\rEng}What's the date?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.00,1:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,10月8号了\N{\rEng}October eighth.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.95,1:06:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5周了  我是9月15号天离开劳伦斯的\N{\rEng}Five weeks. I left Laurens on the fifth of September.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.00,1:06:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直住在那拖车上啊\N{\rEng}You been bunkin' in that?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.45,1:06:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的移动房子\N{\rEng}That's my rollin' home.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.33,1:06:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪里安营扎寨\N{\rEng}Where you been settin' up camp?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.49,1:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在田野里  我晚上休息不赶路\N{\rEng}In the fields. I pull off. I don't travel at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.16,1:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你独自一个人的时候不害怕吗\N{\rEng}Haven't you been scared, being alone?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.62,1:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处都有奇怪的人\N{\rEng}There are weird people everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.62,1:07:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  我参加过二战\N{\rEng}Well, ma'am, I fought in the trenches in World War II.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.40,1:07:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会怕爱荷华州的田野吗\N{\rEng}Why should I be scared of an Iowa cornfield?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.74,1:07:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额\N{\rEng}Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.04,1:07:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们修好机器之前...\N{\rEng}till we get this mower fixed...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.07,1:07:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,何不在我家院子住一晚\N{\rEng}why don't you...ah, bivouac in our yard here?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.70,1:07:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车库里有浴室你可以使用\N{\rEng}There's a bathroom in the garage you can use.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.16,1:07:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真是太慷慨了\N{\rEng}Well, that's awful generous of you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.74,1:07:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的车应该也会同意的\N{\rEng}and I'm sure my machine here is agreeable to that too.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.99,1:07:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢今天帮助我的人们\N{\rEng}Sure wanna thank you folks for helping me today.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.82,1:07:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是要下雨\N{\rEng}There's a lot of rain forecast.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.32,1:07:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用住那个拖车里了\N{\rEng}Sure don't want to get stuck in that trailer.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.99,1:07:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我做一点木匠活  我想你会想要一些新鲜东西\N{\rEng}I...I do a little woodwork. I thought you'd like a few fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.61,1:07:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我女儿是个木匠  她会做小鸟屋\N{\rEng}My daughter does woodwork. She makes birdhouses.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.74,1:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  那太好了\N{\rEng}Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.91,1:08:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你弄好了吗  -我想是的\N{\rEng}-You finished there? -I believe I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.24,1:09:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我想打个电话  -当然可以  进来吧\N{\rEng}-I'm in need of a phone. -Sure. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.94,1:09:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想告诉我女儿我的近况\N{\rEng}I wanna tell my daughter about my recent travels.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.90,1:09:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请进吧\N{\rEng}Sure. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.57,1:09:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不好意思了  你有无绳电话吗\N{\rEng}If it's all the thing with you, do you have a cordless phone?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.82,1:09:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门是开着的  进来吧\N{\rEng}-Door's wide open, come... -I can call from out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.78,1:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你  你可以坐在厨房里打  不用客气的\N{\rEng}Here you go. You're welcome to sit in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.15,1:10:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你需要一些私人空间我们可以离开\N{\rEng}We can leave, if you're lookin' for privacy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.61,1:10:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去比较好  这里的区号也是712吗\N{\rEng}Out here's fine. Is the area code still 712 here?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.45,1:10:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  阿尔文  那样你会拨打到319\N{\rEng}No, Alvin. That hill rolled you into 319.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.69,1:10:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拨打你的地方的区号\N{\rEng}You need to dial one and your area code.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.40,1:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是712  谢谢\N{\rEng}712, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.98,1:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂\N{\rEng}'Hello?'
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.23,1:10:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝\N{\rEng}Rose?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.52,1:10:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸  爸\N{\rEng}Dad?...Dad...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.85,1:10:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到你的声音我太高兴了\N{\rEng}Uh, I'm...so glad to hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.77,1:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修好那个机器要花掉他一大笔钱\N{\rEng}It's gonna cost him a bundle to fix that mower.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.73,1:11:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为他没那么多钱\N{\rEng}I don't think he's got that kinda money.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.44,1:11:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会开着那个机器去埃克塞尔西奥\N{\rEng}I wouldn't drive that thing to Excelsior.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.35,1:11:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁叫它偏偏是个割草机\N{\rEng}It's a lawn mower, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.19,1:11:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的社保支票  啊...是在这里  爸爸\N{\rEng}Uh, your social security cheque? Ah...it's here, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.03,1:11:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝  你能把我的支票传过来吗\N{\rEng}Rose, can you send me my cheque?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.89,1:11:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\rEng}Uh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.15,1:11:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真幸运成功过了那个山\N{\rEng}He's damn lucky he made it down that hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.86,1:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一不小心就送命了  -是啊\N{\rEng}-He could've died easily. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.39,1:11:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不强壮了\N{\rEng}He's none too strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.44,1:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看他走路还要手杖啊\N{\rEng}See how he has to walk with the canes?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.11,1:11:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  爸爸\N{\rEng}OK, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.14,1:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我...\N{\rEng}I...I...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.11,1:11:49.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  好  爸爸  我记下来了  爸爸\N{\rEng}OK, OK, Dad, OK. I...I have a pencil, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.89,1:11:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越靠近密西西比河\N{\rEng}The hillsjust get worse
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.69,1:11:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山路变得更难走了\N{\rEng}the closer you get to the Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.72,1:12:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的  开车送他去吧\N{\rEng}Go ahead and drive him, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.39,1:12:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到锡安山就半天的时间  没什么大不了的\N{\rEng}Mount Zion can't be half a day. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.15,1:12:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丹尼  你人这么好\N{\rEng}You're a good man, Danny Riordan.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.39,1:12:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我当初不顾我妈反对嫁给了你\N{\rEng}And that's why I married you, despite what my mother said.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.98,1:12:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  很好\N{\rEng}Now, shoo!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.23,1:12:16.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸\N{\rEng}Dad?...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.47,1:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你了  爸爸\N{\rEng}I miss you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.56,1:12:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你  露丝\N{\rEng}I love you, Rosie.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.35,1:12:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你  爸爸\N{\rEng}'I love you too, Dad.'
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.44,1:12:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  爸爸\N{\rEng}Uh, bye, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.47,1:12:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\rEng}Bye...Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.81,1:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咳咳\N{\rEng}Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.56,1:13:04.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在厨房煮什么  阿尔文\N{\rEng}What are you cookin' there, Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.02,1:13:06.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢  我在做墨西哥咖啡\N{\rEng}Oh, I'm makin' my Mexican coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.55,1:13:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介意我和你一起吗\N{\rEng}Ah. Mind if I join you?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.14,1:13:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐  铁椅子上吧\N{\rEng}Get you a chair... that iron one there.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.48,1:13:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在自己的院子里变成客人了\N{\rEng}You'll be a guest in your own back yard.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.27,1:13:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟奥尔森双胞胎谈过了  啊...他们估计\N{\rEng}Amm, I talked to the Olsen twins, and, ah...they estimate
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.80,1:13:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修好你的机器差不多250美元\N{\rEng}it'll cost around 250 dollars to get your mower fixed.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.22,1:13:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是它本身的两倍了\N{\rEng}Well, that's twice what it oughta be,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.39,1:13:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜正常的两倍了  是吧\N{\rEng}I guess it's cost they're twice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.97,1:13:45.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你去锡安山吧\N{\rEng}I'd be happy to drive you the rest of the way to Mount Zion.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.76,1:13:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会是一个不错的周日自驾游  我们享受穿过河流\N{\rEng}Be a nice Sunday drive. We enjoy crossin' the river,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.18,1:13:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是现在有五颜六色的树\N{\rEng}especially now with the trees in colour.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.85,1:13:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额  我很感激  但...\N{\rEng}Well, I appreciate that, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.51,1:13:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,...我想独自完成我的旅途\N{\rEng}...I wanna finish this one my own way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.68,1:14:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试这个\N{\rEng}Try this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.01,1:14:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.39,1:14:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文  你知道  在这里和锡安之间\N{\rEng}Well, you know, Alvin, there's a lotta hills
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.72,1:14:26.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有更难走的山路\N{\rEng}bigger than Clairmont's between here and Zion.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.55,1:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使你的割草机再次发动起来\N{\rEng}Even if you get that mower runnin' again,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.72,1:14:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它还是会坏掉\N{\rEng}it may still break down.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.97,1:14:36.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很固执的  你的好意我心领了\N{\rEng}Well, you're a kind man talkin' to a stubborn man.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.51,1:14:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是希望完成由我自己开始的这条路\N{\rEng}I still wanna finish this the way I started.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.97,1:14:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不...\N{\rEng}No, no...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.55,1:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  威尔兰\N{\rEng}Hi, Verlyn.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.80,1:14:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你最近怎么样  -我很好\N{\rEng}-How the heck you doing? -Fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.05,1:14:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错\N{\rEng}Wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.43,1:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在那里\N{\rEng}He's there.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.63,1:15:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们给了你一盘她做的果仁朱古力饼\N{\rEng}Well...they gave you a plate of her brownies.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.01,1:15:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.93,1:15:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么\N{\rEng}How's that for timing?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.68,1:15:15.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她做的朱古力饼\N{\rEng}Janet makes the best brownies...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.75,1:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拉斐特县最好的\N{\rEng}in Lafayette county.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.59,1:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在每年县城比赛中都得奖\N{\rEng}She won prizes every year at the county fair.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.34,1:15:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-嗯...你自便  -谢谢\N{\rEng}-Mmm...help yourself. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.42,1:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是出差的  正要去喝酒\N{\rEng}Mmm...I've been doin' errands and I'm heading for a beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.47,1:15:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你应该和我一起喝酒\N{\rEng}I thought you'd like to join me.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.26,1:15:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经戒酒了  但是...\N{\rEng}Well, I don't drink any more, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.59,1:15:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不能一成不变\N{\rEng}I'm always up for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.80,1:15:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  来吧\N{\rEng}Well, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.51,1:15:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了下那座山时\N{\rEng}Well, I'm ridin' a little higher and a little faster.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.30,1:15:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开的车高了点  快了点\N{\rEng}Except when you came down that hill.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.13,1:16:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在法国戒酒消愁\N{\rEng}I picked up a mournful taste for liquor in France.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.30,1:16:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来后我就喝个不停\N{\rEng}When I came back, I couldn't drink enough of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.14,1:16:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可救药了\N{\rEng}I wasn't worth a stick of stove wood... I was mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.17,1:16:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位牧师帮了我一把\N{\rEng}A preacher helped me put some distance
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.09,1:16:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮了戒了酒  还让我看清了\N{\rEng}between me and the bottle. And he helped me see...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.46,1:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我酗酒的真正原因  战场的噩梦\N{\rEng}the reason I was drinkin', I was seein' all them things here,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.30,1:16:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍不断在脑海涌现\N{\rEng}that I'd seen over there.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.17,1:16:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多人回来后就酗酒了\N{\rEng}Lots of men came back drinkin' hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.72,1:16:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都在努力忘记\N{\rEng}Well...everyone tryin' to forget.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.17,1:17:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一眼就看透\N{\rEng}I can see it in a man right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.72,1:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\rEng}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.17,1:17:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次...\N{\rEng}There was one time...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.12,1:17:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我们正在\N{\rEng}when we just...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.59,1:17:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待10天后的第一顿温暖的肉餐\N{\rEng}Were waiting for the first warm meal in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.09,1:17:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...认为过了最难关\N{\rEng}We...thought we'd seen the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.29,1:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么空袭\N{\rEng}We hadn't had much trouble from the air.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.13,1:17:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那个时候快要\N{\rEng}I was on the rise...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.50,1:17:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升任军需主任\N{\rEng}with the quartermaster,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.92,1:18:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为同胞们争取更多的咖啡\N{\rEng}workin' on more coffee for me and my buddies.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.87,1:18:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一架飞过我们上空的战机\N{\rEng}A stray Fokker came over the treetops...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.33,1:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向伙食营帐投下了燃烧弹\N{\rEng}and dropped an incendiary on the mess tent.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.50,1:18:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所有的战友都...\N{\rEng}All my buddies...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.00,1:18:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德军就在我面前的那座山上...\N{\rEng}The Kraut banked right in front of me on that hill...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.50,1:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我能看见...纳粹党卫军徽章\N{\rEng}and now I can... see the...Swastika.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.33,1:18:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是唯一一件我放不下的事情\N{\rEng}That is one thing that I can't shake loose...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.12,1:18:49.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所有战友的脸庞还是那么年轻\N{\rEng}All my buddies faces are still young.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.04,1:18:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情是  我活得越久  他们失去的光阴也越多\N{\rEng}And the thing is, the more years I have, the more they've lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.29,1:19:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时不止是战友的脸庞\N{\rEng}And it's not always buddies faces that I see,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.96,1:19:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有德军的\N{\rEng}sometime they're German faces.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.58,1:19:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争后期我们射杀稚嫩的孩子\N{\rEng}Near the end we were shooting moon-faced boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.62,1:19:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾是个狙击手\N{\rEng}I was a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.62,1:19:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我成长的地方  要学会怎样射击捕食\N{\rEng}Where I grew up, you learned how to shoot to hunt food.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.46,1:19:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把我派到前线站哨\N{\rEng}They'd post me up front. Darn near ahead of the lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.46,1:19:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直坐着...\N{\rEng}And I'd sit...forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.08,1:19:41.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你坐在那里时你可以看看那是多么精彩的事\N{\rEng}It's an amazing thing what you can see while you're sittin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.50,1:19:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会寻找军官  通讯兵或哨兵\N{\rEng}I'd look for the officers, the radio guys or artillery spotter.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.29,1:19:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时我看见烟雾旁的伏兵\N{\rEng}Sometime I'd spot a gun nest by the smoke
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.78,1:19:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朝它开火\N{\rEng}and I'd fire into it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.62,1:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时只是树木里的一点移动\N{\rEng}Sometime it was just a movement in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.45,1:20:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有一个侦察兵\N{\rEng}We had a scout,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.62,1:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个小伙子\N{\rEng}a little fella...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.29,1:20:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫科茨\N{\rEng}name of Kotz.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.87,1:20:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从密尔沃基来的波兰人\N{\rEng}He was a Polish boy from Milwaukee.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.04,1:20:28.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他侦察做得非常好\N{\rEng}He'd always take recon and he was darn good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.58,1:20:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的侦察救了我们好多次\N{\rEng}We went by his word and he saved our skin many a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.32,1:20:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个小伙子\N{\rEng}He was a little fella...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.08,1:20:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们冲出灌木丛\N{\rEng}We'd broken out of the hedgerows...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.16,1:20:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过空地\N{\rEng}We were making a run across the open
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.37,1:20:55.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到了一片树林\N{\rEng}and we come upon a woods.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.91,1:20:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始交火\N{\rEng}We started drawing fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.79,1:21:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在平时的位置...\N{\rEng}I took my usual position...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.53,1:21:09.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我看见有个东西在移动  慢慢的\N{\rEng}and I saw something moving, real slow like.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.37,1:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等了10分钟  它再次移动时我就开枪了\N{\rEng}I waited ten minutes, it moved again and I shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.49,1:21:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它停止移动了\N{\rEng}The movement stopped.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.49,1:21:27.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天我们发现科茨...头部中枪\N{\rEng}The next day we found Kotz...head shot.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.86,1:21:32.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他从前线侦察回来\N{\rEng}He'd been workin' his way back toward our lines.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.58,1:21:39.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们组的所有人都认为是德国狙击手爆了他的头\N{\rEng}Everyone in the unit thought a German sniper had taken him...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.16,1:21:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都这样认为\N{\rEng}Everyone, all these years.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.65,1:21:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我\N{\rEng}Everyone but me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.49,1:22:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈\N{\rEng}Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.44,1:22:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧  牛逼\N{\rEng}See, Harald...brainiac...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.86,1:22:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用些小工具没花钱就弄好了\N{\rEng}Got the mower assembly free with this here little old wrench...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.44,1:22:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当初说它好不了\N{\rEng}You said it wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.36,1:23:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说它好得很  你觉得呢\N{\rEng}I'd say it worked pretty good. Wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.61,1:23:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮我把它弄出来再说\N{\rEng}So help me slide her out. We can get settled up.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.90,1:23:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零件和人工费  加起来247.80美元\N{\rEng}Uh...I got parts and labour that add up to $247.80.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.23,1:23:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说这是个轻松活儿\N{\rEng}Well, I'd say that's a little heavy for light work.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.74,1:23:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为呢\N{\rEng}Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.74,1:23:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老花眼了  但\N{\rEng}I've got an old man's eyes, but, ah...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.06,1:24:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这新轮胎\N{\rEng}I'm noticin' some new tyre here.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.07,1:24:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  是二手的\N{\rEng}Well, now...ah, we got those off a resell,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.61,1:24:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这个胎面挺好的\N{\rEng}but the treads are good!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.65,1:24:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是按"好"收费还是按"新"收费的\N{\rEng}Well, friend, are you chargin' me for good or for new?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.40,1:24:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额...索瓦尔德\N{\rEng}Ahhhh...Thorvald?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.99,1:24:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额...我们可以微调下价格\N{\rEng}Ahh...we can make an adjustment there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.31,1:24:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为调整的价格应该是30元左右\N{\rEng}Well, I think the adjustment should be about thirty dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.69,1:24:28.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你记下来了吗\N{\rEng}Is that what your pencil's sayin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.15,1:24:30.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  这个人工费...\N{\rEng}And, ah...about the labour...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.78,1:24:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激你花在这上面的时间...\N{\rEng}I appreciate that you boys have done some real time on this...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.69,1:24:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  不得不说当一对双胞胎在一起干活时\N{\rEng}of course, a man's gotta ask when he's workin' with twins -
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.11,1:24:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是一对争吵不休的\N{\rEng}especially a bickerin' pair -
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.20,1:24:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有多少时间是用在了争吵上\N{\rEng}how much workin' was fightin'?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.56,1:24:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\rEng}He got that right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.61,1:24:51.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  丹尼\N{\rEng}Shut up, Danny.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.32,1:24:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是根据我今天愉快的经历来判断的话\N{\rEng}If I was to judge by this joyous affair I saw today,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.02,1:25:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看能给人工费打个八折\N{\rEng}I would calculate maybe 20 per cent taken off the labour.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.27,1:25:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的吗  先生\N{\rEng}Anything else, mister?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.90,1:25:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是本地人  但在我们那儿\N{\rEng}Well, I'm not from these parts, but where I come from,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.98,1:25:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这爱阿华州的油是稍贵\N{\rEng}I would say that that was a little rich for Iowa oil.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.78,1:25:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油不收钱\N{\rEng}Take the oil, no charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.43,1:25:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真慷慨  太感谢了\N{\rEng}Well, that's a splendid offer and I do appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.40,1:25:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少合适\N{\rEng}What's the tally?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.78,1:25:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,额...额...\N{\rEng}Ah...ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.57,1:25:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,187元\N{\rEng}Hundred and eighty seven?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.52,1:25:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成交\N{\rEng}Done.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.89,1:25:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你们  我要继续赶路\N{\rEng}Thanks to you boys, I'm gonna get this rig back on the road.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.52,1:25:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直开着它穿过爱荷华州\N{\rEng}I've drove it all the way across Iowa and I'm hopin' it holds on
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.85,1:25:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望它能坚持到威斯康辛州  我哥哥住那儿\N{\rEng}till I get to Wisconsin. My brother lives there.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.69,1:25:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经10年没见着他了\N{\rEng}I haven't seen him in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.81,1:25:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一个人比与你年纪相近的哥哥\N{\rEng}There's no one knows your life better
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.60,1:26:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更了解你了\N{\rEng}than a brother that's near your age.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.40,1:26:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他比世界上任何一个人更\N{\rEng}He knows who and what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.15,1:26:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解你是怎样的\N{\rEng}better than anyone on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.39,1:26:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和哥哥上次见面时  互相说了些不堪入耳的话\N{\rEng}My brother and I said some... unforgivable things
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.90,1:26:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我尽量不去想\N{\rEng}the last time we met, but, I'm tryin' to put that behind me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.48,1:26:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这口气确实很难咽下去\N{\rEng}And this trip is a hard swallow...of my pride,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.60,1:26:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望我别太晚\N{\rEng}I just hope I'm not too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.06,1:26:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兄弟始终还是兄弟\N{\rEng}A brother's a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.98,1:26:52.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯...\N{\rEng}Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.98,1:26:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该休息去了\N{\rEng}Guess I'll be turning in.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.47,1:27:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会  额...早上再见  在你走之前\N{\rEng}I'll, ah...see you in the morning, then, before you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.06,1:27:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会很早启程\N{\rEng}I'm gonna leave awful early.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.94,1:27:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢你对我这个陌生人所做的一切\N{\rEng}I wanna thank you for your kindness to a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.26,1:27:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很荣幸你在这儿  阿尔文\N{\rEng}It's been a genuine pleasure havin' you here, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.39,1:27:33.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有空常来信\N{\rEng}Write to us, sometime.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.27,1:27:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会的\N{\rEng}I will.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.38,1:32:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我注意到你的篝火\N{\rEng}I noticed your campfire.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.46,1:32:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你带了些晚餐...土豆泥  肉卷\N{\rEng}I brought you some dinner... Mashed potatoes, meat loaf.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.29,1:32:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢  我已经吃过晚餐了\N{\rEng}Well, thank you kindly. I've had my dinner,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.50,1:32:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来聊聊天吧\N{\rEng}but would you join me for a while?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.66,1:32:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊\N{\rEng}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:44.21,1:32:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\rEng}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.84,1:32:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不介意我擅自闯入\N{\rEng}I hope you don't mind me trespassin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.79,1:32:59.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  一点也不\N{\rEng}Oh, no, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.12,1:33:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个好选地\N{\rEng}Made a fine choice.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.71,1:33:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你扎营的地方是中西部最古老的\N{\rEng}You're camped next to one of the oldest cemeteries
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.21,1:33:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,墓地之一的旁边  法国天主教捕兽\N{\rEng}in the Midwest. French Catholic trappers.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.21,1:33:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法国耶稣会传教士  -其中的两个人\N{\rEng}-The Marquette party. -Two of his men.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.04,1:33:16.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不说\N{\rEng}I couldn't help but notice
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.91,1:33:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那不寻常的交通工具\N{\rEng}the rather unusual mode of transport.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.42,1:33:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  你不是第一个说它的人  神父\N{\rEng}Well, you're not the first person to notice that, Padre.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.29,1:33:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛有问题  我不能开车\N{\rEng}My eyes are bad. I can't drive.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.58,1:33:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢坐别人开的大巴\N{\rEng}I don't like someone else drivin' the bus,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.67,1:33:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要到我哥哥那儿去\N{\rEng}and I need to get to my brother's.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.66,1:33:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有道理\N{\rEng}Fair enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.91,1:33:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哪\N{\rEng}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.62,1:33:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离他很近了  我几乎可以感觉到他\N{\rEng}Well, he's so close, I can practically feel him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.42,1:33:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡安山\N{\rEng}Mount Zion.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:44.84,1:33:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫什么\N{\rEng}What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.49,1:33:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史崔特  赖尔\N{\rEng}Lyle Straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.33,1:33:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是几周前中风的那个\N{\rEng}Is he that fella that came in with a stroke some weeks ago?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.49,1:33:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识他吗\N{\rEng}Do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.12,1:34:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为那医院工作\N{\rEng}I work at the hospital in Boscobel.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.25,1:34:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得他入院\N{\rEng}I remember him comin' in.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.33,1:34:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为...他住在我的教区  所有我留意了他\N{\rEng}Caught my attention because...he lives in my parish.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.58,1:34:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是浸信会教友\N{\rEng}Well, he's a Baptist.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.12,1:34:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有告诉我\N{\rEng}Oh, I believe he told me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.46,1:34:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我说了我一些东西\N{\rEng}Told me a few things, matter of fact,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.66,1:34:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他没提他有一个兄弟\N{\rEng}but he didn't mention having a brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.58,1:34:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个闹翻不做兄弟有很久了\N{\rEng}Well, neither one of us has had a brother for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.29,1:34:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你看到过他  他一切还好吗\N{\rEng}So, you saw him? Is he all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.75,1:34:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只见过他那一次然后就没有然后了\N{\rEng}I only saw him that once and I haven't heard anything more.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.83,1:34:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖尔和我小时候关系很好\N{\rEng}Well, Lyle and I grew up as close as brothers could be.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.24,1:35:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在明尼苏达州的一个农场生活\N{\rEng}We were raised on a farm in Moorhead, Minnesota.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.95,1:35:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们努力工作  爸妈为农场付出了所有心血\N{\rEng}We worked hard. My mom and dad darn near killed themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.41,1:35:09.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能有好收成\N{\rEng}tryin' to make that farm work.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.66,1:35:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我和赖尔却忙中偷闲\N{\rEng}And me and Lyle would make games out of our chores.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.91,1:35:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们幻想些比赛然后打赌\N{\rEng}We'd dream up somethin' about racin' and wagerin'
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.95,1:35:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能忘了寒冷\N{\rEng}do anything to keep our mind off the cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.83,1:35:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是冷\N{\rEng}Lord, it was cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.46,1:35:30.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们晚上都睡在院子里\N{\rEng}He and I used to sleep out in the yard
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.24,1:35:33.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要没有瓢泼大雨\N{\rEng}every summer night, if it wasn't pourin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:33.45,1:35:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冬季有九个月  夏天特别的短暂\N{\rEng}Nine months of winter, we couldn't get enough summer.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.86,1:35:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳下山后我们就上床了\N{\rEng}We'd bunk down when the sun went down.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.20,1:35:45.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直聊天直到睡去\N{\rEng}We'd talk to each other until we went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.95,1:35:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们谈论星星还有\N{\rEng}We'd talk about the stars and whether there might be
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.74,1:35:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太空中是否有像我们一样的外星人\N{\rEng}somebody else like us out in space,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.65,1:35:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想去的地方等等\N{\rEng}places we wanted to go and...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.74,1:36:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我们过得很快乐\N{\rEng}it made our trials seem smaller.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.74,1:36:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从小无话不说\N{\rEng}Yeah, we pretty much talked each other through growin' up.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.70,1:36:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论你们之间发生了什么\N{\rEng}Oh, whatever happened between you two?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.36,1:36:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如撒该和亚伯兄弟的老故事\N{\rEng}Story as old as the Bible. Cain and Abel.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.82,1:36:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愤怒  虚荣\N{\rEng}Anger, vanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.28,1:36:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上酒精\N{\rEng}You mix that together with liquor, and...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.95,1:36:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就成就了十年不相往来的兄弟俩了\N{\rEng}you've got two brothers who haven't spoken in ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.12,1:36:47.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是什么让我和赖尔反目成仇的\N{\rEng}Well, whatever it was that made me and Lyle so mad...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.45,1:36:50.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不再是问题了\N{\rEng}don't matter any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.95,1:36:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要合好\N{\rEng}I wanna make peace.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.83,1:36:56.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和他坐在一起\N{\rEng}I wanna sit with him,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.99,1:36:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起看星星...\N{\rEng}look up at the stars...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.11,1:37:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我们以前那样...\N{\rEng}like we used to do...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.24,1:37:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前那样\N{\rEng}so long ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.16,1:37:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生...\N{\rEng}Well, sir...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.95,1:37:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福你\N{\rEng}I say ''Amen'' to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.66,1:38:15.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEng}Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.03,1:38:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很多年没有喝酒了\N{\rEng}I haven't had a drink in a lot of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.90,1:38:39.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在想来一瓶啤酒\N{\rEng}Now I'm gonna have me a beer.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.61,1:38:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么口味\N{\rEng}What flavour?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.11,1:38:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米勒简版的口味如何\N{\rEng}What does a Miller's Lite taste like?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.24,1:38:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你\N{\rEng}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.07,1:39:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-味道怎样  -不错\N{\rEng}-How's it taste? -It's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.99,1:39:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用找了  -谢谢\N{\rEng}-Keep the change. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.81,1:39:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这拉风的座驾  爬山能行么\N{\rEng}It's an interesting rig you got outside. Get up the hill OK?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.73,1:39:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这山 还有200个这样的山\N{\rEng}That hill and 200 more just like it.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.02,1:39:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从多远来的\N{\rEng}How far did ya come?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.11,1:39:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱荷华州\N{\rEng}From Iowa.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.36,1:39:23.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是向着赖尔  史崔特那里来的\N{\rEng}I'm headed for Lyle Straight's place.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.73,1:39:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱荷华州  我的天  你一定渴了吧\N{\rEng}Iowa! My God, you must be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.23,1:40:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一杯吧\N{\rEng}Another beer?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.48,1:40:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了已经\N{\rEng}This will do me fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.43,1:40:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能告诉我赖尔家怎么走吗\N{\rEng}I wonder could you point me to Lyle's place?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.89,1:40:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很久没见过他了\N{\rEng}I haven't seen him in an awful long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.44,1:40:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走61号公路到"W"公路\N{\rEng}Well, you just...ah, cross 61 here, on ''W'',
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.89,1:40:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后走"W"到杂草路接着走到雷明顿路\N{\rEng}Take ''W'' on down to Weed Road and then on to Remington Road.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.98,1:40:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖尔家就在你的右手边\N{\rEng}On your right will be Lyle's place.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.64,1:40:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他在那儿\N{\rEng}If he's there that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.18,1:43:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样\N{\rEng}How you doin'...?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.76,1:43:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太好\N{\rEng}Not too good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.30,1:43:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点累了\N{\rEng}This thing'sjust tired.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.72,1:43:19.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么我能帮你的吗\N{\rEng}Is there anything I can do to help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.51,1:43:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  不要我了吧\N{\rEng}Well, I don't know. It just quit on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.26,1:43:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为何不再试试\N{\rEng}Why don't you try her again?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.55,1:43:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去赖尔  史崔特那里\N{\rEng}I'm headin' to Lyle Straight's place.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.92,1:45:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖尔\N{\rEng}Lyle!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.01,1:45:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赖尔\N{\rEng}Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.22,1:45:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔文\N{\rEng}Alvin?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.33,1:46:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐下  阿尔文\N{\rEng}Sit down, Alvin.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.33,1:47:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就骑那玩意跑来看我的啊\N{\rEng}Did you ride that thing all the way out here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.04,1:47:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  赖尔\N{\rEng}I did, Lyle.
